<div ng-controller="safeCtrl">	
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12">
				<div class="text-left">
					<h1 class="fauna org text-left">Beware of Unauthorized Resellers</h1>
				</div>
				<p>Soundcast wireless audio products and speakers are sold in the United States through a network of authorized dealers & retailers appointed by Soundcast. 
				Soundcast dealers and retailers have been selected based on their ability to properly represent, support and provide quality customer service. Some of these 
				dealers may have Internet sites on which they have been authorized by Soundcast to sell our products. Soundcast provides a warranty on products sold only 
				by our authorized dealers.</p><br>
				<p><b>Make sure you purchase from an authorized Soundcast Dealer.</b> Visit our <a href="/pages/find-retailers">Find a Retailer</a> page, enter your zip code (US only) and click “Search”. </p><br>
				<p>Please call 1-800-722-1293 to speak with a customer service specialist or email <a href="mailto:support@goSoundcast.com">support@goSoundcast.com</a> should you have any questions or need 
				assistance finding the nearest authorized Soundcast dealer or online retailer.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12">
				<div class="text-left">
					<h1 class="fauna org text-left">Authorized Online Dealers</h1>

				</div>	
				<p>The following dealers have been authorized to sell Soundcast products online:</p>
				<br>
				
					<div class="row">
						<div ng-repeat="logo in logos">
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3">
							{% raw %}
								<img ng-src="{{logo.img}}" class="img-responsive {{logo.classe}}"/>
							{% endraw %}
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<br>
					<div class="row">
						<div ng-repeat="logo in logos2">
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3">
							{% raw %}
								<img ng-src="{{logo.img}}" class="img-responsive {{logo.classe}}"/>
							{% endraw %}
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>					
				
				<br>

				<p>A note about Amazon.com: Soundcast does NOT sell directly to Amazon.com (listings with sold by Amazon.com), but does authorize a small number of 
				our dealer partners to sell via the Amazon Marketplace (Fulfilled by Amazon). These listings will indicate the “seller name” and “shipped by Amazon.com”. 
				Soundcast aggressively monitors and addresses un-authorized selling on Amazon Marketplace.</p>

				<p>Contact <a href="mailto:sales@goSoundcast.com">sales@goSoundcast.com</a> if you have any questions or would like to inquire about becoming an authorized online dealer.</p>

			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12">
				<div class="text-left">
					<h1 class="fauna ruby text-left">Unauthorized Online Dealers</h1>
				</div>	
				<br>
				<p>The following online companies are <b>NOT AUTHORIZED</b> to sell Soundcast products: (list not all inclusive)</p>
