		<br>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12">
				<p>Unfortunately, Soundcast products are sometimes sold by companies that are not authorized or trained to do so. Goods sold by these unauthorized 
				companies are NOT purchased from Soundcast; instead they are acquired from a variety of other sources, and many times damaged, used, or altered 
				from their original condition. This is true even when unauthorized companies state that the product is “new”. We are using our best efforts to prohibit these 
				companies from taking advantage of consumers. We encourage you to use diligence and common sense when making your Soundcast purchase.</p>

			</div>
